name: 7Lights Insignia
description:
7... the number of God in Supreme Mathematics. All chakras and their corresponding Orishas... the
Lights. The light will be spread across the community through music and arts to attack mental illnesses, such as anxiety and depression, at its source; to attack oppression at its foundation and to build a better understanding of the human existence and how our existence correlates with the entire universe. Sometimes the truth is uglier than the mind wants to accept but, its always better digested over dope ass 808's and captivating melodies.Sometimes beauty is misunderstood and miscalculated, but the raw voice of the struggle cannot be unheard.

Peace, Love & Lights
